About this item

  • Apple MFi CertifiedUGREEN Lightning to 3.5mm car audio cables are certified by Apple to meet rigid iPhone requirements and ensures completely and securely connect with your Apple devices.
  • Compatible device: The lightning car audio cables are compatible with Apple iPhone 12/12 Mini/12 Pro/12 Pro Max/11 Pro Max/11 Pro/11/XS/XS Max/XR/X/8/8 Plus/7/7 Plus, iPad Pro /Air /mini, iPod touches 6th generation and so on. Supports iOS 12/11/10 and earlier Operation System
  • High performanceThe aux stereo audio cable builts with dual-shielding, corrosion-resistant 24K gold-plated 3.5mm connectors. ensuring reliability and reducing signal loss and noise. The braided cable with good touch feeling makes it beautiful and durable.
  • Multi applicationEasy to connect your Apple Devices to car stereos, home stereos, portable speaker, headphone, Hi-Fi, computer or anything else with a 3.5mm input jack.
  • Flexible braided jacket: Nylon braided aux cable has excellent wear resistance and protects the inner conductor from the risk of cable breakage. Scratch-resistant aluminum housing not only gives the aux cable a nice look but also does a good job of dissipating heat.

Product Description

UGREEN Apple Certified Nylon-Braided & Aluminum Aux Headphone Cable Compatibility with iPhone

Why choose UGRENN Lightning to 3.5mm Male Aux Cable?

Apple MFi

Apple MFi certification ensures ongoing compatibility with iPhone after iOS updates.

Clear Sound

Nickel-plated 3.5mm connector and high-polished aluminum connectorensure to transmit sound stably and seamlessly. No fuzzy noise.

Ultra Durable & Tangle-Free

High-quality nylon braid material makes the aux cable for iPhone in the car a more durable and long serving time. You can wind it without having to worry about knots or kinks.

Convenient to take

It is very lightweight, easy to store, not winding, not knotted, can be foldable, easy to carry around, great for home and travel.

Multi-Shielding for Excellent Sound Quality

Braid and AL-Foil shielding and shielded enameled copper conductors provide better corrosion resistance and signal transmission, ensuring high fidelity sound quality without sound degradation and current noise

Widely Compatibility:

iPhone Models: iPhone 12/12 Pro/12 mini/12 Pro Max/SE 2020/11 Pro / iPhone 11 Pro Max / iPhone 11 / XS / XS Max / XR / X / 8 / 8 Plus / 7/ 7 Plus/ 6S/ 6S Plus / 6 / 6 Plus / SE / 5S / 5C / 5

iPad Models: iPad (7th generation) / iPad 9.7"(6th generation 2018) / iPad (2017) / iPad 4 / iPad 3 / iPad 2 / iPad 1 iPad Pro 12.9" / 10.5"(2nd generation), iPad Pro 12.9" / 9.7"(1st generation) iPad Air 3 / iPad Air 2 / iPad Air (1st generation) iPad mini 5 / mini 4 / mini 3 / mini 2 / mini

iPod Models: iPod touch (7th generation) / iPod touch (6th generation)

3.5mm Audio:

Portable speakers

Receivers

Car stereos

NOTE:

  • It only supports IOS 10.3.1 and later.
  • It doesn't compatible with 2018 iPad Pro 11" / 12.9" which has a USB C interface
  • NOTE: For iPhone 7 and iPhone 7 Plus, make sure it has been updated to iOS 10.3.1 or later

Apple MFi Certified

Certified by Apple to meet rigid iPhone requirements and ensures completely and securely connect with your Apple devices.

Soft Nylon Braid

Soft Nylon Braid cable body makes it soft and durable

Plug & Play

Just insert the lightning head into your Apple devices and insert the 3.5mm male,like car stereo, Hi-Fi, normal speaker and so on.

      Question:
      Will this work with an old stereo receiver from the 80s?
      Answer:
      No. The headphone plug-in on your receiver is for output only. All of the inputs are on the back. You need a lightning to dual RCA (R&L) adapter.
